data.description: Price improvement!! Nestled in the heart of Harahan, Louisiana, this charming property offers a rare combination of comfort and versatility. The main residence, a cozy 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom home, exudes warmth with its inviting living spaces and thoughtful layout, perfect for those who appreciate a blend of classic design and practical living. Adding to the property's appeal is an additional dwelling unit (16x20), presenting a unique opportunity for rental income, a guest house, or a private home office. Set in a serene neighborhood, this property not only promises a peaceful living environment but also provides easy access to local amenities and the vibrant community of Harahan. Whether you're looking for a family home with space for expansion or an investment opportunity, this property is a true gem waiting to be discovered.
